    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Refers to small manufactured articles that are decorative or amusing and intended primarily for personal or household use. They are typically characterized by being of little utilitarian value and for being appealing primarily due to the newness of their design.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
